  "content": "<ol><li></li></ol><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\"\"><ol><li><br></li><li><span style=\"font-weight: bold;\">炼（理）五星</span></li><li><br></li></ol><div><img src=\"//cdnimg-v2.gamekee.com/wiki2.0/images/w_1602/h_1059/50364/497891/2024/3/24/979929.png\" data-width=\"1602\" data-height=\"1059\"></div><div><br></div><div>获取方式：新手第一抽获取</div><div><br></div><div>推荐源器：前期带攻势4件套+疾驰套，后期带洞悉4件套+追击两件套</div><div><br></div><div><img src=\"//cdnimg-v2.gamekee.com/wiki2.0/images/w_454/h_597/50364/497891/2024/3/24/705635.png\" data-width=\"454\" data-height=\"597\" style=\"height: 217.013px; width: 165.031px;\"> <img src=\"//cdnimg-v2.gamekee.com/wiki2.0/images/w_453/h_558/50364/497891/2024/3/24/732221.png\" data-width=\"453\" data-height=\"558\" style=\"height: 215.563px; width: 175px;\"> <img src=\"//cdnimg-v2.gamekee.com/wiki2.0/images/w_459/h_598/50364/497891/2024/3/24/42068.png\" data-width=\"459\" data-height=\"598\" style=\"height: 217.572px; width: 167px;\"> <img src=\"//cdnimg-v2.gamekee.com/wiki2.0/images/w_456/h_555/50364/497891/2024/3/24/426310.png\" data-width=\"456\" data-height=\"555\" style=\"height: 219.734px; width: 180.536px;\"></div><div><br></div><div>主属性：核心带主词条选择暴击率，爆伤，攻击力加成，平衡双爆，最佳双爆配比1:2</div><div><br></div><div>推荐智壳：R推荐打气绵绵，SR推荐玉藻童子，SSR推荐歧路，万魔法典</div><div><br></div><div><img src=\"//cdnimg-v2.gamekee.com/wiki2.0/images/w_146/h_196/50364/497891/2024/3/24/189058.png\" data-width=\"146\" data-height=\"196\"> <img src=\"//cdnimg-v2.gamekee.com/wiki2.0/images/w_148/h_198/50364/497891/2024/3/24/616612.png\" data-width=\"148\" data-height=\"198\"> <img src=\"//cdnimg-v2.gamekee.com/wiki2.0/images/w_145/h_197/50364/497891/2024/3/24/577951.png\" data-width=\"145\" data-height=\"197\"> <img src=\"//cdnimg-v2.gamekee.com/wiki2.0/images/w_145/h_201/50364/497891/2024/3/24/505079.png\" data-width=\"145\" data-height=\"201\"></div><div><br></div><div>推荐潜能加点：一技能推荐点到等级5，核心技能，二技能推荐点到等级3，三技能推荐点到等级4</div><div>简介：前期新手就送的群伤c，推图很好用，队伍带上增伤拐，清副本推主线都是很好的选择。</div><div><br></div><ol><li>格雷（虚）四星</li><li><br></li></ol><div><img src=\"//cdnimg-v2.gamekee.com/wiki2.0/images/w_1577/h_1040/50364/497891/2024/3/24/711761.png\" data-width=\"1577\" data-height=\"1040\"></div><div><br></div><div>获取方式：新手赠送</div><div><br></div><div>推荐源器：前期带攻势套+疾驰套，后期带追击4件套+时光两件套，副词条歪到20命中可不带时光带洞悉</div><div><br></div><div><img src=\"//cdnimg-v2.gamekee.com/wiki2.0/images/w_459/h_642/50364/497891/2024/3/24/723398.png\" data-width=\"459\" data-height=\"642\" style=\"height: 230.784px; width: 165px;\"> <img src=\"//cdnimg-v2.gamekee.com/wiki2.0/images/w_459/h_598/50364/497891/2024/3/24/662038.png\" data-width=\"459\" data-height=\"598\" style=\"height: 229.289px; width: 176px;\"> <img src=\"//cdnimg-v2.gamekee.com/wiki2.0/images/w_456/h_555/50364/497891/2024/3/24/21444.png\" data-width=\"456\" data-height=\"555\" style=\"height: 230.033px; width: 189px;\"> <img src=\"//cdnimg-v2.gamekee.com/wiki2.0/images/w_462/h_642/50364/497891/2024/3/24/515579.png\" data-width=\"462\" data-height=\"642\" style=\"height: 229.286px; width: 165px;\"></div><div><br></div><div>主属性：核心主词条选择暴击率，爆伤，攻击力加成，需要歪一点效果命中</div><div><br></div><div>推荐智壳：R推荐风滚草，SR推荐蝎尾女皇，不羁科学，SSR推荐万魔法典，黑旗</div><div><br></div><div><img src=\"//cdnimg-v2.gamekee.com/wiki2.0/images/w_146/h_198/50364/497891/2024/3/24/752303.png\" data-width=\"146\" data-height=\"198\"> <img src=\"//cdnimg-v2.gamekee.com/wiki2.0/images/w_141/h_197/50364/497891/2024/3/24/202212.png\" data-width=\"141\" data-height=\"197\"> <img src=\"//cdnimg-v2.gamekee.com/wiki2.0/images/w_139/h_201/50364/497891/2024/3/24/829368.png\" data-width=\"139\" data-height=\"201\"> <img src=\"//cdnimg-v2.gamekee.com/wiki2.0/images/w_141/h_198/50364/497891/2024/3/24/657282.png\" data-width=\"141\" data-height=\"198\"> <img src=\"//cdnimg-v2.gamekee.com/wiki2.0/images/w_145/h_201/50364/497891/2024/3/24/437911.png\" data-width=\"145\" data-height=\"201\"></div><div><br></div><div>推荐潜能加点：一技能没必要点，点的话点到等级3，二技能点满，三技能等级3足够</div><div>简介：前期非常好用的角色，二技能全队加暴击率，三技能全体减防，记得副词条多刷点速度，伤害是次要</div><div><br></div><ol><li>千明 （理）四星</li><li><br></li></ol><div><img src=\"//cdnimg-v2.gamekee.com/wiki2.0/images/w_1569/h_994/50364/497891/2024/3/24/708611.png\" data-width=\"1569\" data-height=\"994\"></div><div><br></div><div>获取方式：卡池抽取</div><div><br></div><div>推荐源器：前期带疾驰4件套+涌泉两件套，后期带治愈4件套或者护佑4件套+涌泉两件套</div><div><br></div><div><img src=\"//cdnimg-v2.gamekee.com/wiki2.0/images/w_459/h_598/50364/497891/2024/3/24/456407.png\" data-width=\"459\" data-height=\"598\" style=\"height: 231.453px; width: 177.654px;\"> <img src=\"//cdnimg-v2.gamekee.com/wiki2.0/images/w_460/h_649/50364/497891/2024/3/24/667723.png\" data-width=\"460\" data-height=\"649\" style=\"height: 231.383px; width: 164px;\"> <img src=\"//cdnimg-v2.gamekee.com/wiki2.0/images/w_461/h_648/50364/497891/2024/3/24/489106.png\" data-width=\"461\" data-height=\"648\" style=\"height: 230.525px; width: 164px;\"> </div><div><br></div><div>主属性：核心主词条如果带的治愈4件套就选择生命加成，效果抵抗，如果带的护佑4件套，就选择暴击率和生命加成</div><div><br></div><div>推荐智壳：R推荐月光，SR推荐真理，SSR推荐黑旗，万魔法典</div><div><br></div><div><img src=\"//cdnimg-v2.gamekee.com/wiki2.0/images/w_143/h_196/50364/497891/2024/3/24/7142.png\" data-width=\"143\" data-height=\"196\"> <img src=\"//cdnimg-v2.gamekee.com/wiki2.0/images/w_145/h_196/50364/497891/2024/3/24/513189.png\" data-width=\"145\" data-height=\"196\"> <img src=\"//cdnimg-v2.gamekee.com/wiki2.0/images/w_141/h_198/50364/497891/2024/3/24/767679.png\" data-width=\"141\" data-height=\"198\"> <img src=\"//cdnimg-v2.gamekee.com/wiki2.0/images/w_145/h_201/50364/497891/2024/3/24/72706.png\" data-width=\"145\" data-height=\"201\"></div><div><br></div><div>推荐潜能加点：一技能没必要点，二技能至少点到等级3，三技能至少等级3，可以点到等级5</div><div><br></div><div>简介：不需要任何练度的奶妈，上场就有治疗量，被动纸人给队友减伤，能大大缓解生存压力。新手奶妈不二选择</div><div><br></div><ol><li>克洛斯（异）五星</li><li><br></li></ol><div><img src=\"//cdnimg-v2.gamekee.com/wiki2.0/images/w_1584/h_988/50364/497891/2024/3/24/189119.png\" data-width=\"1584\" data-height=\"988\"></div><div><br></div><div>获取方式：卡池抽取</div><div><br></div><div>推荐源器：前期带疾驰4件套和涌泉两件套，后期带时光4件套+疾驰两件套</div><div><br></div><div><img src=\"//cdnimg-v2.gamekee.com/wiki2.0/images/w_459/h_598/50364/497891/2024/3/24/25312.png\" data-width=\"459\" data-height=\"598\" style=\"height: 272.292px; width: 209px;\"> <img src=\"//cdnimg-v2.gamekee.com/wiki2.0/images/w_460/h_649/50364/497891/2024/3/24/781911.png\" data-width=\"460\" data-height=\"649\" style=\"height: 273.709px; width: 194px;\"> <img src=\"//cdnimg-v2.gamekee.com/wiki2.0/images/w_462/h_642/50364/497891/2024/3/24/137423.png\" data-width=\"462\" data-height=\"642\" style=\"height: 276.532px; width: 199px;\"></div><div><br></div><div>主属性：核心主词条选择效果命中，效果抵抗，生命加成或者防御加成，需要堆高效果命中</div><div>推荐智壳：R随便带，SR推荐怪盗喵，蝎尾女王，SSR推荐万魔法典，黑旗</div><div><br></div><div><img src=\"//cdnimg-v2.gamekee.com/wiki2.0/images/w_145/h_197/50364/497891/2024/3/24/352910.png\" data-width=\"145\" data-height=\"197\"> <img src=\"//cdnimg-v2.gamekee.com/wiki2.0/images/w_141/h_198/50364/497891/2024/3/24/776018.png\" data-width=\"141\" data-height=\"198\"> <img src=\"//cdnimg-v2.gamekee.com/wiki2.0/images/w_145/h_201/50364/497891/2024/3/24/458625.png\" data-width=\"145\" data-height=\"201\"></div><div><br></div><div>推荐潜能加点：一技能推荐点到3级，二技能推荐点到3级，三技能推荐3级，有条件的点满</div><div>简介：顶级辅助，无论是pvp还是pve都有大用，集增伤，推条，拉条，加攻，降伤的角色，目前最优秀的辅助！</div><div><br></div><ol><li>卡奇（理）三星</li><li><br></li></ol><div><img src=\"//cdnimg-v2.gamekee.com/wiki2.0/images/w_1578/h_1004/50364/497891/2024/3/24/227561.png\" data-width=\"1578\" data-height=\"1004\"></div><div><br></div><div>获取方式：新手赠送</div><div><br></div><div>推荐源器：疾驰4件套+时光两件套</div><div><br></div><div><img src=\"//cdnimg-v2.gamekee.com/wiki2.0/images/w_459/h_598/50364/497891/2024/3/24/217207.png\" data-width=\"459\" data-height=\"598\" style=\"height: 276.2px; width: 212px;\"> <img src=\"//cdnimg-v2.gamekee.com/wiki2.0/images/w_462/h_642/50364/497891/2024/3/24/118686.png\" data-width=\"462\" data-height=\"642\" style=\"height: 276.532px; width: 199px;\"></div><div><br></div><div>主属性：核心主词条选择效果命中，生命值加成，效果抵抗，副词条主要选择速度</div><div><br></div><div>推荐智壳：有啥带啥，不挑</div><div><br></div><div>推荐潜能加点：一技能可以不点，二技能也可以不点，三技能可以点到等级3</div><div><br></div><div>简介：三星之光，目前唯一的拉条辅助的含金量，前期非常好用，也非常好养。</div><div><br></div><ol><li>弥瑟亚（恒定）五星</li><li><br></li></ol><div><img src=\"//cdnimg-v2.gamekee.com/wiki2.0/images/w_1573/h_990/50364/497891/2024/3/24/402411.png\" data-width=\"1573\" data-height=\"990\"></div><div><br></div><div>获取方式：抽卡获取</div><div><br></div><div>推荐源器：前期带攻势套+疾驰套，后期带洞悉4件套+追击两件套</div><div><br></div><div><img src=\"//cdnimg-v2.gamekee.com/wiki2.0/images/w_454/h_597/50364/497891/2024/3/24/491499.png\" data-width=\"454\" data-height=\"597\" style=\"height: 199.877px; width: 152px;\"> <img src=\"//cdnimg-v2.gamekee.com/wiki2.0/images/w_459/h_598/50364/497891/2024/3/24/41806.png\" data-width=\"459\" data-height=\"598\" style=\"height: 199.333px; width: 153px;\"> <img src=\"//cdnimg-v2.gamekee.com/wiki2.0/images/w_453/h_558/50364/497891/2024/3/24/765701.png\" data-width=\"453\" data-height=\"558\" style=\"height: 197.086px; width: 160px;\"> <img src=\"//cdnimg-v2.gamekee.com/wiki2.0/images/w_456/h_555/50364/497891/2024/3/24/604924.png\" data-width=\"456\" data-height=\"555\" style=\"height: 195.954px; width: 161px;\"></div><div><br></div><div>主属性：核心主词条选择暴击，爆伤，攻击力加成，平衡双爆，最佳双爆配比1:2</div><div><br></div><div>推荐智壳：R推荐打气绵绵，SR推荐玉藻童子，SSR推荐歧路，万魔法典</div><div><br></div><div><img src=\"//cdnimg-v2.gamekee.com/wiki2.0/images/w_675/h_214/50364/497891/2024/3/24/159312.png\" data-width=\"675\" data-height=\"214\"></div><div><br></div><div>推荐潜能加点：一技能至少点到等级2，推荐点满。二技能至少点到等级3，三技能至少点到等级3</div><div><br></div><div>简介：目前最强群伤大c，拥有强大的自拐能力，下限极高，普攻能易伤，技能带斩杀，大招群伤无视防御和自身无敌，纯数值怪。</div><div><br></div><ol><li>缇亚马特（虚）五星</li><li><br></li></ol><div><img src=\"//cdnimg-v2.gamekee.com/wiki2.0/images/w_1573/h_969/50364/497891/2024/3/24/606391.png\" data-width=\"1573\" data-height=\"969\"></div><div><br></div><div>获取方式：抽卡获取</div><div><br></div><div>推荐源器：前期带涌泉4件套+疾驰两件套，后期带戍卫4件套+涌泉两件套</div><div><br></div><div><img src=\"//cdnimg-v2.gamekee.com/wiki2.0/images/w_460/h_649/50364/497891/2024/3/24/912198.png\" data-width=\"460\" data-height=\"649\" style=\"height: 265.243px; width: 188px;\"> <img src=\"//cdnimg-v2.gamekee.com/wiki2.0/images/w_459/h_598/50364/497891/2024/3/24/582084.png\" data-width=\"459\" data-height=\"598\" style=\"height: 265px; width: 203.403px;\"> <img src=\"//cdnimg-v2.gamekee.com/wiki2.0/images/w_457/h_648/50364/497891/2024/3/24/194875.png\" data-width=\"457\" data-height=\"648\" style=\"height: 263.737px; width: 186px;\"> </div><div><br></div><div>主属性：核心主词条选择生命值加成，暴击率。词条上主堆生命值，次堆速度和暴击率</div><div><br></div><div>推荐智壳：R推荐月光，SR推荐真理，不羁科学，SSR推荐黑旗，万魔法典</div><div><br></div><div><img src=\"//cdnimg-v2.gamekee.com/wiki2.0/images/w_143/h_196/50364/497891/2024/3/24/635479.png\" data-width=\"143\" data-height=\"196\"> <img src=\"//cdnimg-v2.gamekee.com/wiki2.0/images/w_145/h_196/50364/497891/2024/3/24/672061.png\" data-width=\"145\" data-height=\"196\"> <img src=\"//cdnimg-v2.gamekee.com/wiki2.0/images/w_139/h_201/50364/497891/2024/3/24/105.png\" data-width=\"139\" data-height=\"201\"> <img src=\"//cdnimg-v2.gamekee.com/wiki2.0/images/w_145/h_201/50364/497891/2024/3/24/711093.png\" data-width=\"145\" data-height=\"201\"> <img src=\"//cdnimg-v2.gamekee.com/wiki2.0/images/w_141/h_198/50364/497891/2024/3/24/303791.png\" data-width=\"141\" data-height=\"198\"></div><div><br></div><div>推荐潜能加点：一技能至少点到等级3，推荐点满，二技能至少点到等级3，三技能随便点点就行</div><div><br></div><div>简介：集合烧血c，护盾，奶妈，坦克为一体的多功能角色，六边形战士，pvp，pve都特别好用</div><div><br></div><ol><li>莉莉斯（虚）五星</li><li><br></li></ol><div><img src=\"//cdnimg-v2.gamekee.com/wiki2.0/images/w_1547/h_1003/50364/497891/2024/3/24/171366.png\" data-width=\"1547\" data-height=\"1003\"></div><div><br></div><div>获取方式：抽卡获取</div><div><br></div><div>推荐源器：前期带涌泉4件套+疾驰两件套，后期带时光4件套+涌泉或者疾驰两件套</div><div><br></div><div><img src=\"//cdnimg-v2.gamekee.com/wiki2.0/images/w_460/h_649/50364/497891/2024/3/24/589421.png\" data-width=\"460\" data-height=\"649\" style=\"height: 292px; width: 206.956px;\"> <img src=\"//cdnimg-v2.gamekee.com/wiki2.0/images/w_459/h_598/50364/497891/2024/3/24/939747.png\" data-width=\"459\" data-height=\"598\" style=\"height: 291.399px; width: 223.656px;\"> <img src=\"//cdnimg-v2.gamekee.com/wiki2.0/images/w_462/h_642/50364/497891/2024/3/24/947219.png\" data-width=\"462\" data-height=\"642\" style=\"height: 289.92px; width: 208.625px;\"></div><div><br></div><div>主属性：核心主词条带效果命中，生命值加成，副词条优先效果命中，其次生命值</div><div><br></div><div>推荐智壳：R推荐月光，SR推荐不羁科学，蝎尾女皇，SSR推荐万魔法典，黑旗</div><div><br></div><div><img src=\"//cdnimg-v2.gamekee.com/wiki2.0/images/w_143/h_196/50364/497891/2024/3/24/879382.png\" data-width=\"143\" data-height=\"196\"> <img src=\"//cdnimg-v2.gamekee.com/wiki2.0/images/w_141/h_197/50364/497891/2024/3/24/634199.png\" data-width=\"141\" data-height=\"197\"> <img src=\"//cdnimg-v2.gamekee.com/wiki2.0/images/w_139/h_201/50364/497891/2024/3/24/880632.png\" data-width=\"139\" data-height=\"201\"> <img src=\"//cdnimg-v2.gamekee.com/wiki2.0/images/w_145/h_201/50364/497891/2024/3/24/188005.png\" data-width=\"145\" data-height=\"201\"> <img src=\"//cdnimg-v2.gamekee.com/wiki2.0/images/w_141/h_198/50364/497891/2024/3/24/591655.png\" data-width=\"141\" data-height=\"198\"></div><div><br></div><div>推荐潜能加点：一技能可以不点，二技能至少点到等级3，推荐点满，三技能至少点到等级3。</div><div><br></div><div>简介：目前最离谱的推条类角色，自身还能多动晕人，pvp超级恶心，pve也很强，抽到必练角色之一。</div><div><br></div><ol><li>风见一宵（虚）四星</li><li><br></li></ol><div><img src=\"//cdnimg-v2.gamekee.com/wiki2.0/images/w_1552/h_942/50364/497891/2024/3/24/7252.png\" data-width=\"1552\" data-height=\"942\"></div><div><br></div><div>获取方式：抽卡获取</div><div><br></div><div>推荐源器：前期带疾驰4件套+随意生存两件套，后期带疾驰4件套+时光两件套</div><div><br></div><div><img src=\"//cdnimg-v2.gamekee.com/wiki2.0/images/w_459/h_598/50364/497891/2024/3/24/156224.png\" data-width=\"459\" data-height=\"598\" style=\"height: 269.686px; width: 207px;\"> <img src=\"//cdnimg-v2.gamekee.com/wiki2.0/images/w_462/h_642/50364/497891/2024/3/24/110933.png\" data-width=\"462\" data-height=\"642\" style=\"height: 273.753px; width: 197px;\"></div><div><br></div><div>主属性：核心主词条带效果命中，效果抵抗，副词条优先速度，其次生存和命中</div><div><br></div><div>推荐智壳：R推荐月光，SR推荐不羁科学，蝎尾女皇，SSR推荐万魔法典和黑旗</div><div><br></div><div><img src=\"//cdnimg-v2.gamekee.com/wiki2.0/images/w_824/h_221/50364/497891/2024/3/24/415391.png\" data-width=\"824\" data-height=\"221\"></div><div><br></div><div>推荐潜能加点：一技能必点等级三，有条件点满；二技能至少点等级3，有条件点满；三技能至少点等级3，有条件点满</div><div><br></div><div>简介：四星最强辅助，普攻有推条，技能能推条+加敌方cd，大招还能全体拉条和减我方cd，抽到必练，pve发挥不显著，pvp发挥非常亮眼，从一堆五星里都能脱颖而出。</div></span></span><div></div>",
